{"tid":948141,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己隻公仔有靈性","createTime":"2018-12-19T21:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T10:14:57.000Z","uid":63626,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e97c31101d41f0e8cf6005079aca324c5817fb38","tid":948141,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:17:42.000Z","msg":"通常公仔攬開都會有朕味，而且仲幾香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個隻以前都係咁<br />\n但唔知點解，近年變左模式<br />\n放置左一排會無左朕味（例如放學返黎），攬返上手一陣先會返返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係佢見到我返黎，所以好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者有冇人可以用科學角度解釋到呢個現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2581813105613ace55ac49b0840f2a2752af93","tid":948141,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:19:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你浸味"},{"pid":"6cd93abfc886a883b4ba19470e14d37188c09da2","tid":948141,"uid":41368,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:28:44.000Z","msg":"其實係你陣汗味"},{"pid":"12db7d9873978878bc5202c0eb82db38b4c5a2ca","tid":948141,"uid":63626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b2581813105613ace55ac49b0840f2a2752af93","tid":948141,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:19:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你浸味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:31:59.000Z","msg":"我諗唔會係我朕味，可能係公仔本身既味/我+公仔溝埋一齊既味<br />\n如果多公仔既人，會知隻隻公仔既味都係唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有幾隻公仔係同一個地方買，但身上既味都唔同<br />\n可能係用料問題啦，但我係去同一間鋪買同一款公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf3933c6c273b60bceb8d496975a0cec6995d54","tid":948141,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6cd93abfc886a883b4ba19470e14d37188c09da2","tid":948141,"uid":41368,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:28:44.000Z","msg":"其實係你陣汗味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T21:32:28.000Z","msg":"冬天邊有汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e425644bb6c8db518360d892db50fe2169f1fb8","tid":948141,"uid":189347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T00:46:54.000Z","msg":"我都有隻公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細細個岩岩讀小一果陣屋企人買比我到以家23歲隻公仔都一定要放床頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d655cf8fb2bba45624930ee07beb589c699f1a0","tid":948141,"uid":75959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"我d 腦魔公仔一排無見，講係2個月，變曬毛巾味，以前2個月唔見都仲係我陣味，係咪法力喪失<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b46b9c591ee3340d7c77d71917120c8de137b32","tid":948141,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"附左野"},{"pid":"efb36cc2d304f018d8d9ad85fee84491aea2f553","tid":948141,"uid":108756,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6b46b9c591ee3340d7c77d71917120c8de137b32","tid":948141,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"附左野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhzLPCN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhzLPCN.png&h=ca85312d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3e90a41edbbc07be300dd3f64bac097b16bb53e","tid":948141,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"科學角度: 你個鼻開始有問題"},{"pid":"074b9ca74c2d90bd5ac308dcfb3218e2b96edae9","tid":948141,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"死GAY佬玩毛公仔"},{"pid":"4914e458dae0d027a2b059f1188e19cb9d654b94","tid":948141,"uid":33154,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"有啊<br />\n自從之前無聊玩完一個人捉謎藏<br />\n次次起身<br />\n隻公仔都會出現係我枕頭隔離望住我<br />\n明明我已經燒左佢"},{"pid":"7cfb3913ab7c54e7d019da5d6d609b135e75b267","tid":948141,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"放係床頭幫我驅魔"},{"pid":"4634af5b508a3d7ff27fdfcc12f0dfa7fc9f53e5","tid":948141,"uid":61840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"有公仔冇發過噩夢，之前有晚農曆7月合埋對眼見到好多恐怖野，即刻拎幾隻公仔擺陣，跟住就一覺訓到天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2699ed73c875bb58715704631ba24aa6bc7a32","tid":948141,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"睇你擺咩位姐<br />\n頭，腳，格甩底都唔同味啦"},{"pid":"46557a9c46b093756086350e1ca657098a186d42","tid":948141,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"朕乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a15ccca93196ae82d80e7f19cd730a0a786cdd2","tid":948141,"uid":34411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2629c776d76222a941addab35846b936951c946b","tid":948141,"uid":34411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d5d0110865e21a86dc65672d8ce60e771367468","tid":948141,"uid":145345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"有無人鍾意同屋企d熊仔講野<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/CdJPwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/CdJPwU</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e475b11b010ae0f2db658d86d7aad758dd0d813a","tid":948141,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d655cf8fb2bba45624930ee07beb589c699f1a0","tid":948141,"uid":75959,"like":4,"dislike":